        <heading>1002.  Requirement of original</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1002.  Requirement of original
To prove the content of a writing, recording, or photograph, the original writing, recording, or photograph is required, except as otherwise provided by this Code or other legislation.</p>
        </content>
